# Template for .env. Copy to `.env` and fill in real values; `.env` is
# gitignored, this template is checked in. Anything that goes into ctx via
# os.Getenv during integration tests / dev runs lives here.
#
# .env 模板。复制为 `.env` 后填真值；`.env` 已 gitignore，本模板进 git。
# 集成测试 / 本地起服务 通过 os.Getenv 读取的变量都在这里登记。

# DeepSeek (used by infra/llm integration tests + chat scenario when
# user's api_keys table is empty).
# DeepSeek（用于 infra/llm 集成测试 + 用户 api_keys 表为空时的 chat 场景兜底）
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
